# Semaphore

Compress data into the fewest possible characters.
Ideal for JWTs.

For example...

```
Base64 encoded

10,568 B


Encoded with "SAFER ASCII"

HvtXXTKXKXKXKTuXTtXKXKZTtTuX######KX#v!!Hp#kJznf28p2MkJznf28p2z6AbS7okg6AmJW59gs1jE2IXQ5adpCA8IhxwehOiaaQyzK04bkeidAdWvrgEJPAWrG!TS02Vu5PYN!2ofH491DVE7rZs0cpya3UvESTpoh!6YFXQzU3EFmtscVD!CQQsJzqsG!D4j91V6QefNw6N3rGIE#DauTCYbThis!Is!1!Big!Long!alphanumeric!Sentence!with!numbers!and!spaces!and!stuff!like!that#05YOMh2vtRJvbecLS0tRIc
330 B

Encoded with "SAFER ASCII" and Base64 Encoded

440 B
```
